{"id": 1804, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪种淘宝店铺会给你体面而值得信赖的感觉？", "description": "淘宝店铺不是便宜货的代名词，现如今人们都会根据哪些细节筛选出一家有高级感的店？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 25740, "comment_count": 42, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170717180832gYEy3acBUH9kpDXJ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-26T17:00:18Z", "questions": [{"id": 2624, "title": "哪种淘宝店铺会给你体面而值得信赖的感觉？", "content": "哪种淘宝店铺会给你体面而值得信赖的感觉？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 222416, "content": "极简店铺装修！封面像超市促销单一样的就显得很low", "image": "img/option/option/20170717181130coXsmO0NS6jMQZKU.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222417, "content": "商品展示就平铺没模特", "image": "img/option/option/20170717181140ARqIjKMVyZhuJzbe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222420, "content": "有模特也要不咋笑的那种，万万不能出现网红脸", "image": "img/option/option/20170717182426drlCYPhIOSyaBq9o.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222418, "content": "商品描述简单不忽悠，排版清爽", "image": "img/option/option/20170717182116AIUOegsdNBHSkhm2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222421, "content": "商品不多，隔几个月上新一次，现货很快就会被抢光", "image": "img/option/option/20170717183051QP5ml0OdLFwvgzr3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222422, "content": "除了售后没有客服全程自助购物的高冷型店铺", "image": "img/option/option/20170717183225VeJGvY3k2E4ZOfFi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222423, "content": "交流的时候不说“亲”、“哈尼”而说“您”", "image": "img/option/option/20170718113257Tcns1zd52WCA8FSl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222424, "content": "不怎么参与购物节打折活动 ", "image": "img/option/option/20170718113345DdTekLUaqz3JY9NW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222425, "content": "不会送压根没啥用的廉价赠品", "image": "img/option/option/20170718113718ZTQzXnwWNdIxih16.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}